        <ul>
            <li><strong>Facial Recognition and Mapping:</strong> They analyze facial features and movements to create a digital mask</li>
            <li><strong>Voice Synthesis:</strong> They can replicate voice patterns to create artificial speech</li>
            <li><strong>Movement Analysis:</strong> They replicate body movements and gestures for realistic animation</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Potential Harms of Deepfakes</h3>
        <p>Deepfakes are frequently used for harmful purposes, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Misinformation:</strong> Creating false narratives that can influence public opinion</li>
            <li><strong>Election Manipulation:</strong> Falsely depicting candidates saying or doing things</li>
            <li><strong>Social Engineering:</strong> Creating convincing impersonations to gain trust</li>
            <li><strong>Fraud:</strong> Impersonating individuals for financial or other gains</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

